        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/54624050-once-and-future-wife">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3609552656" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11655032302373392077"><strong>Interesting</strong><br/><br/>This was such an interesting book. It kept me captivated, I felt like I was right there in the book. I felt like the ending wasn’t quite complete though. I still have so many questions! I hope the author has plans to continue this story. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


